				Verant:  I'm completely behind the 'spirt' of the new Licensing Agreement, but I do also agree with some people's concerns with the level of access that we are 'Oking' when we click Agree.  I believe you should reword the agreement.  Perhaps something similiar to:<BR>
<BR>
